Package com.intellij.psi

Class PsiReferenceRegistrar

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.psi.PsiReferenceRegistrar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserDataHolder
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PsiReferenceRegistrarImpl

    public abstract class PsiReferenceRegistrar
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserDataHolder
    Allows to register reference providers for specific locations.

    The locations are described by ElementPatterns. If a pattern matches some PSI element, then the corresponding PsiReferenceProvider.getReferencesByElement(PsiElement, com.intellij.util.ProcessingContext) is executed, from which one can return the references whose PsiReference.getElement() is the same as the first parameter of PsiReferenceProvider.getReferencesByElement(PsiElement, com.intellij.util.ProcessingContext).
